# ─────── Generated ───────
# Note for Flutter: we intentionally commit *.g.dart and *.freezed.dart
# because the CI pipeline (`.github/workflows/mobile.yml`) does not run
# `build_runner` before `flutter analyze` / `flutter test`. The alternative
# (adding a build-runner step to every job) would triple the CI runtime for
# no measurable benefit — generated file diffs are easy to review and stay
# in sync with their source via a single `dart run build_runner build
# --delete-conflicting-outputs` pre-commit step documented in CLAUDE.md.
*.mocks.dart

# ─────── Logs ───────
*.log
logs/

# ─────── Docker ───────
.docker/
